				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Between 1hs and 2hs for a paladin, or Sk, they both have pros and cons<BR>
<BR>
1hs: fast and low on damage, best to inturrput casters, horrible when you fight an enemy with a damage shield, then you take too much dmg for doing so little each swing<BR>
<BR>
2hs: slow and strong on damage, best to kill a mob with a damage shield, so you wont take much dmg by dmg shield if you hit it, but it's horrible to inturrupt casters, usually you cant unless you turn auto attack off, and turn it on right when the caster cast again.<BR>
<BR>
In my opinin, 2hs is better because when your fighting a enemy with dmg shield, it's no prob, fighting a caster, make sure you have a haste item anytime soon, so you swing and attack strongly =)
